Package: libcoil
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Internal OpenRTM library
 Internal OpenRTM library which should only be used in
 in coordination with openrtm-c++.
 .
 This package contains the library binary.


