Package: libopenrtm-aist-c++
Architecture: any
Depends: libcoil (= ${binary:Version}), ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python (>= 2.6)
Description: Component-oriented robotics system development platform
 Development platform allowing robotics system design by writing
 RT-components and connecting them together.
 .
 This package contains the C++ version of this software.

